latestIgtvVideos.caption:
@rotary_cherryblossom_shillong presents a short clip for World Breastfeeding Week, #august #2021 
Special thanks to our Past District Governor Dr. Das, Rotarian @vansha_choudhury , Rotarian @iaia_anette , @mewan_mylz from @thehillspeople and the entire Rotary Club Cherryblossom Team for the support, love and generosity for making this positive and friendly video montage happen. May it reach the masses and educate them further. Because the children are the reason for a healthy future! 

Regards,
President, Melanie Pariat
